OL,3,CChurch to start hosting heavy metal
OL,4,Cmusic concerts
OL,6,FSt Mary Redcliffe Church in Bristol is
OL,7,Fhoping to host its first heavy metal
OL,8,Fconcert at the beginning of 2025.
OL,10,FThe idea started last August when doom
OL,11,Fmetal bands, Pantheist and Ard,
OL,12,Fperformed with David Pipe, the
OL,13,Fcathedral organist at the Diocese of
OL,14,FLeeds, at Huddersfield Town Hall.
OL,16,FThe performance was featured on Radio
OL,17,F4's Sunday Worship which prompted
OL,18,Fdozens of churches to explore the idea
OL,19,Fof pairing heavy metal with a pipe
OL,20,Forgan.
