OL,6,FJoe Cryan, director of music at St
OL,7,FMary Redcliffe, is hoping this new
OL,8,Fsound will welcome more people to the
OL,9,Fchurch.
OL,11,FHe said: "We're looking at
OL,12,Fdiversifying what our offering is.
OL,13,FWe're always thinking, how can we
OL,14,Freflect what Bristol looks and sounds
OL,15,Flike today.
OL,17,F"Bristol is becoming more and more a
OL,18,Fsecular city. Bringing new people into
OL,19,Fthe church to hear the organ in a new
OL,20,Fand exciting way is something I'm
OL,21,Freally keen to do."
