OL,6,FIt's thought he may have played the
OL,7,FHarris and Byfield organ that was
OL,8,Ffitted in the church at that time -
OL,9,Fsome of whose surviving pipework was
OL,10,Fincorporated into the modern organ.
OL,12,FOf course, the idea of playing heavy
OL,13,Fmetal music in a church isn't for
OL,14,Feveryone.
OL,16,FIn February, Canterbury Cathedral had
OL,17,Fto defend its decision to host a
OL,18,Fsilent disco after a petition calling
OL,19,Fon the event to be cancelled received
OL,20,Fmore than 1,500 signatures.
