OL,6,FMr Cryan said he understands why there
OL,7,Fmight be "a bit of conflict" over the
OL,8,Fissue but insists the idea is "an
OL,9,Fabsolute positive".
OL,11,F"If we've got a heavy metal band
OL,12,Fcoming in, then it's going to bring in
OL,13,Fnew voices, new perspectives and new
OL,14,Fideas on what the church can be," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FAt least seven metal bands have
OL,18,Fcontacted St Mary Redcliffe so far to
OL,19,Fexpress their interest in performing
OL,20,Fthere.
